Defendant in custody on WRIT.
The defendant is sentenced to the Wisconsin State Prison System for a total of seven (7) years.  That is three (3) years initial confinement followed by four (4) years extended supervision on each count, concurrent and concurrent with the sentence presently serving.
The Court finds the defendant eligible for both the Challenge Incarceration Program and the Substance Abuse Program.
Conditions of extended supervision:
1) Pay restitution of $800.00 to MX Mega Store, Att: David Klein at 3208 Menasha Avenue, Manitowoc, WI;
2) AODA assessment and follow through;
3) Pay court costs;
4) pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC;
5) no contact with MX Mega Store;
6) maintain absolute sobriety;
7) no association with any known drug dealers or users;
8) defendant is to use only one doctor to prescribe medications and only one pharmacy to fill prescriptions, unless approved by the agent;
9) Maintain fulltime employment or work search;
10) Assessment, treatment, counseling as deemed appropriate by the Departments assessment process;
11) Undergo a mental health assessment if determined necessary by the agent.
The defendant has credit for 34 days.  (from PO hold on 07-24-15 until his sentencing after revocation of probation on 08-27-15)
